column4: NSLOCTEXT("[DF3DF5924544FBE77DAE328E2DCCFC94]", "7831FF5549835194CEF2C78F0717306E", "I will teach you about the common sense in our world.")
NSLOCTEXT("[DF3DF5924544FBE77DAE328E2DCCFC94]", "9BD22DCD49109CD7500162B89B47D846", "There are twenty four hours a day and there is morning, day and night.")
NSLOCTEXT("[DF3DF5924544FBE77DAE328E2DCCFC94]", "0E17930B4E1DB22E006B4B9A27207C95", "You may feel the pace is quick.")
NSLOCTEXT("[DF3DF5924544FBE77DAE328E2DCCFC94]", "94213A4443C18D6AFF6960B984083319", "There are thirty days a year. Month? What\'s that? Seasons? Can you eat that?")
NSLOCTEXT("[DF3DF5924544FBE77DAE328E2DCCFC94]", "A2596ACC458113CFC8198B83D5CF6563", "Of course we have money. The unit is a bit. You can never have too much money.")
NSLOCTEXT("[DF3DF5924544FBE77DAE328E2DCCFC94]", "60A99ED5471E27CA7D3EA09373570BBD", "When you say \'city\' on this island, that means here.")
NSLOCTEXT("[DF3DF5924544FBE77DAE328E2DCCFC94]", "72F978B8493275B4EB481E9B0FAA073E", "But there are other small villages and towns.")
NSLOCTEXT("[DF3DF5924544FBE77DAE328E2DCCFC94]", "01C9897F40EAD8CBA9D48BA7581481C9", "On the clock, the yellow dot is hours and the needle is minutes.")
NSLOCTEXT("[DF3DF5924544FBE77DAE328E2DCCFC94]", "5EED05C9483C463F7647A698A3287988", "Up is Midnight and Down is Noon.")
NSLOCTEXT("[DF3DF5924544FBE77DAE328E2DCCFC94]", "FCCAC1734155E859A6A33193862FBC2A", "The purple part on the right is morning and it shows 04:00 to 08:00.")
NSLOCTEXT("[DF3DF5924544FBE77DAE328E2DCCFC94]", "856165E848E42F2DEE6EE39AF339C074", "The orange part on the left means late afternoon. It shows 16:00 to 20:00.")
NSLOCTEXT("[DF3DF5924544FBE77DAE328E2DCCFC94]", "258D07BB44A4AE05AD63B69CC85F437C", "Digimon are active at certain times of day.")
NSLOCTEXT("[DF3DF5924544FBE77DAE328E2DCCFC94]", "4BC3AFDE47144155AA24E1B20D2CB8F9", "Most of them get up in the morning and sleep at night, but some are opposite.")
NSLOCTEXT("[DF3DF5924544FBE77DAE328E2DCCFC94]", "238460204D7C65A7234A689864B8282B", "If you can\'t meet the Digimon you wish, try a different time of day.")
